text: The Families Act is a narrowly tailored solution to a lose-lose situation when it comes to keeping families together at the border. https://t.co/xzg6vcVmGp

The Families Act addresses family separations by overriding the court decision that has produced the current lose-lose situation and by providing the resources to expeditiously adjudicate asylum claims. https://t.co/LYxvohJ7xC

The Families Act would:
✔️Secure our borders
✔️Enforce our immigration laws
✔️Maintain reasonable asylum standards
✔️Keep asylum-seeking families together
